            "question": "Can I Gift Kush Queen CBD Bath Bombs As Part Of A Self-Care Package?",
            "answer": "<p>CBD bath bombs make thoughtful and functional gifts that fit into a wide range of wellness-focused occasions. Kush Queen offers several curated sets designed to simplify gifting while still delivering high-quality, targeted products. Here's how these options work well for self-care and sharing:</p><h3><strong>CBD Bath Bomb Bundles For Easy Gifting</strong></h3><p>Kush Queen offers pre-assembled bath bomb bundles with varying scents and strengths. These sets take the guesswork out of choosing individual products while offering variety within a single package. They are ideal for birthdays, holidays, or wellness-themed care kits.</p><h3><strong>Holiday Best Sellers Set As A Ready-Made Gift</strong></h3><p>The Holiday Best Sellers Set features two Relax CBD bath bombs and one Relieve CBD bath bomb, each with 250mg of full-spectrum CBD. This curated trio offers both mood-focused and body-targeted benefits, making it a complete and thoughtful gift option. With pH-friendly, vegan ingredients and handmade quality, it reflects a commitment to comfort and clean wellness.</p><h3><strong>Adding Melt CBD Lotion For A Complete Body Collection</strong></h3><p>Including melt CBD lotion alongside bath bombs rounds out a self-care gift set with both soaking and post-bath care. This combination introduces the benefits of topical CBD in two different formats. Together, they offer a more complete experience centered on relaxation and skin support.</p><h3><strong>Wellness-Focused Gifts That Align With Modern Routines</strong></h3><p>Gifting hemp bath bombs reflects a shift toward wellness-based, intentional giving. These products align with routines that prioritize recovery, mindfulness, and rest. Their growing popularity makes them a relevant and appreciated addition to any self-care package.</p><h3><strong>How CBD Gifts Pair With Other Product Types</strong></h3><p>CBD bath bombs can be paired with other wellness items like THC gummies for a full-spectrum gift